        <div class="share-photos">
            <h2>Share Your Photos With Us</h2>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <p>We'd love to see your photos from our wedding day! Please share them using our wedding hashtag or upload them to our shared album.</p>

            <div class="share-options">
                <div class="share-option">
                    <h3>Wedding Hashtag</h3>
                    <p class="hashtag">#NathaliaAndBart2025</p>
                    <p>Use this hashtag when posting on Instagram or Facebook</p>
                </div>

                <div class="share-option">
